            As the Minister is aware, we remain concerned about this new legislation and its impact on service, on public funds&#x2014;and on the Armed Forces, which will be raised next in Amendment No. 110&#x2014;and on various other bodies that we shall discuss in Amendments Nos. 115, 116 and 116A. I beg to move.
          </p>
