            I want to deal with the point picked up by the noble Lord, Lord Borrie, in his commentary on Clause 11(4). He suggested that it repeated something that was already present. The subsection does not repeat anything. The higher education corporations were removed from Schedule 2 by the <a href="/acts/teaching-and-higher-education-act-1998">Teaching and Higher Education Act 1998</a>. The amendment seeks to reinsert higher education corporations in the schedule of exempt charities.
